{100}{}{Oswald}
{200}{}{You see a grimy looking trader.}
{210}{}{This greasy looking man is wearing a red shirt, with a tag that reads, "Hi! My name is Oswald." You don't know why he's wearing a name tag.}
{1000}{}{Predialogue installations}
