{2000}{}{Welcome weary traveller! I am Oswald! Magnificent trader extraordinaire! But I'm not selling, no, no, no. I'm buying! I purchase only the finest of handmade weapons and armor from the wanderers of the wasteland. Interested in doing a little trading?}
{2010}{}{I've completed one of your bulk order requests...}
{2020}{}{Can I sell you something?}
{2030}{}{That's great! I'm a trader myself, what are you looking for?}
{2040}{}{So you aren't selling anything? That's too bad.}
{2050}{}{Not right now, but maybe later.}
{3000}{}{Only the finest of gear. Metal Armor MK2, Advanced Flamethrowers, M60's, Miniguns, Laser Rifles, Super Stimpaks, Rocket Launchers, Sniper Rifles, and Combat Armor. For this, six of any, I will pay you a good price.}
{3010}{}{I see, no easy task. But if the money's good, I'll trade.}
{4000}{}{No, my friend. Only buying. My clients are many, and require a large amount of disposable weapons, and armor. }
{4010}{}{Okay, thanks.}
{4020}{}{Who are your clients?}
{5000}{}{The NCR army. They have caps, trust me, and I'll throw you half of what I make. You won't find a better deal anywhere else.}
{5010}{}{Sounds lucrative. Very lucrative.}
{6000}{}{Excellent! General Kilgorian will be pleased! Very well done, my friend! }
{7000}{}{Oh? And what have you ready to trade?}
{7010}{}{6x Metal Armor MK2.}
{7020}{}{6x Advanced Flamers.}
{7030}{}{6x M60's.}
{7040}{}{6x Miniguns.}
{7050}{}{6x Laser Rifles.}
{7060}{}{6x Super Stimpaks.}
{7070}{}{6x Rocket Launchers.}
{7080}{}{6x Sniper Rifles.}
{7090}{}{6x Combat Armor.}
{7100}{}{Nothing, actually. Sorry about that.}
{8000}{}{You? Unfortunately not. You don't seem to be experienced enough, sorry.}
{100000001}{}{Better wash the counter again...}
{100000002}{}{That's 5 caps buddy. Hey did you hear me? Cough em' up.}
{100000003}{}{Better change the keg...}
{100000004}{}{RotGut? You drink that shit?}
{100000005}{}{Domestic? I got B.E.E.R buddy, do you want one or not?}
{100000006}{}{Fuckin' dust is getting everywhere. Hey close the fuckin' door!}
{100000007}{}{I swear if the next asshole doesn't tip. Ima' shoot somebody!}
{100000008}{}{I got bottles, I got shots, and I got a bat behind the counter for the retards. Your not a retard are you?}
{100000009}{}{Uh-huh, yeah that's nice buddy. You don't say...What? Of course I'm listening...}
{100000010}{}{That's 5 caps. FIVE CAPS Tribal! F.I.V.E! }
{100000011}{}{Shut up and order a fuckin' beer already!}
{100000012}{}{I swear if I have to serve another drunk, I'm getting the shotgun!}
{100000013}{}{Look the keg went dry, and it's going to be another month until the caravan shows up again.}
{100000014}{}{Really? You don't say, buy another drink or get out!}
{100000015}{}{What? I'm on break.}
{100000016}{}{Be right with ya'}
{100000017}{}{Have a sit stranger. I'll be with you in a moment.}
{100000018}{}{When do we close? Uh, when the place get's shot up, that's when!}
{100000019}{}{We're fresh outta' cold beer, sorry. You'll just have to drink it warm.}
{100000020}{}{RotGut? No man, go make that shit yourself! I wouldn't drink it!}

